videos.description: Justin Fields is stripped of the ball and it rolls out the back of the end zone to give Miami (OH) a 2-0 lead on Ohio State.

videos.description: J.K. Dobbins creates some space and sprints into the end zone for a 26-yard Buckeyes' touchdown.

videos.headline: Dobbins runs outside for an Ohio State touchdown

videos.description: Justin Fields airs it out to K.J. Hill, who makes a tackler miss, then walks into the end zone for a 53-yard Buckeyes' touchdown.

videos.headline: Fields goes deep to a wide-open WR for an Ohio State score

videos.headline: Fields follows up passing TD with rushing score

videos.description: Justin Fields pulls it back on the option and dives in the end zone for another Buckeyes' touchdown.

videos.headline: Fields keeps it for his 2nd rushing TD

videos.description: Justin Fields fakes the handoff, then moves to his right and tosses a 13-yard touchdown to Chris Olave.

videos.headline: Fields rolls out and hits Olave for an Ohio State TD

videos.description: Justin Fields puts it where his receiver can make a play, and Binjimen Victor hauls in the 30-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Victor makes nice grab on Fields' 3rd TD pass

videos.description: Justin Fields throws a 10-yard touchdown on a pinpoint pass to Chris Olave to add to Ohio State's rout of Miami (OH).
